  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this study is to determine whether teplizumab (MGA031) infusions lead
      to greater reductions in insulin requirements in conjunction with near normal blood sugar
      control compared to placebo in patients recently diagnosed with type 1 diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
